boxEditor.heading: Subscription Editor
csaPage.about: Community Supported Agriculture is a concept, which is among other things, trying to connect a consumer directly with a farmer. One method to achieve this, is to subscribe to shares of farm produce (boxes). Most common is a weekly subscription with handover on agreed pickup point. In general the more shares you prepay the lower the price per share.
csaPage.about2: Below you can see farm's subscription offerings, choose a pickup point in Pickup Points section and in case of interest contact the farmer through one of the contacts listed in Farm section.
csaPage.aboutš: Níže si můžete prohlédnout nabídku odběrů, v sekci Odběrová Místa si vybrat odběrové místo a v případě zájmu kontaktovat farmáře na jeden z kontaktů uvedených v sekci Farma.
